{
  "stem": "280.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was-- this was the world's best kept secret.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody ever heard of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although the-- the Slovak Jews were taken much sooner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But never, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] at least not us in-- in Hungary or not us in Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said, they are-- we are going to be taken to some-- we didn't think that we are going to be taken out of the country.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the country, to some place, because-- to-- to work for the war effort.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are, you know, like the Japanese or here, we were not people who were trusted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and they put us to work, to have forced, free labor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But not something like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now-- then we are-- we were taken into a barrack, which was a long wooden building, quite a few.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were taken into the C lager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were housed in some bunks, bunk beds like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the months in Auschwitz, how many months were they?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From June until October-- the end of October was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The months in Auschwitz passed with being woken up at dawn and dragged-- taken out from the barracks, and lined up in front of the barracks, and stood there for hours.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a form of torture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a climate, sometimes during the day [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the early mornings were cold like-- and I tell you, again, with my shaven head, it was something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were standing-- we were lined up, I guess in rows of six or seven.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you had to stay straight and put your best face on everything before-- because if you were noticed that you-- you were were weak or you were sick or you didn't feel good, you were in mortal danger.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
